      "repair_reason": "Human review and contributor action are needed because the PR has a security-sensitive allowlist gap and the required real behavior proof is still insufficient for the central custom/LanceDB path.; Needs attention: The PR expands a hidden sub-agent tool surface and still allows at least two non-memory plugin-backed tools through config.toolsAllow.; Review finding: [P2] Deny plugin-backed core tools in recall allowli... (sha=a446692edd810ce8ce8f0aabdcc3cd720e22260d)",
